Package org.ndeftools.wellknown.handover

Class Summary
AlternativeCarrierRecord Alternative Carrier Record.
CollisionResolutionRecord Collision Resolution Record.
ErrorRecord Error record.
HandoverCarrierRecord Handover Carrier Record

The Handover Carrier Record provides a unique identification of an alternative carrier technology in Handover Request messages when no carrier configuration data is to be provided.
HandoverRequestRecord Handover Request Record

The Handover Request Record identifies a list of possible alternative carriers that the Handover Requester device would be able to use for further communication with the Handover Selector.
HandoverSelectRecord Handover Select Record

The Handover Select Record identifies the alternative carriers that the Handover Selector device selected from the list provided within the previous Handover Request Message.
 

Enum Summary
AlternativeCarrierRecord.CarrierPowerState  
ErrorRecord.ErrorReason An 8-bit field that indicates the specific type of error that caused the Handover Selector to return the Error Record
HandoverCarrierRecord.CarrierTypeFormat This is a 3-bit field that indicates the structure of the value of the CARRIER_TYPE field.
